{"type":"message","id":"967befa1","parentId":"00b552b4","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:00:36.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-26 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1779735636880}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b71fc1e","parentId":"967befa1","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:01:02.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me craft a poetic, first-person reflection that weaves together the technical details about the VN TikTok API issue and Amazon Hair Claws data analysis, the Sorftime MCP API integration, and the Feishu bitable writing process. I should keep it between 80-180 words, in a gentle, whimsical tone, mixing technical and tender observations.\n\nLet me write this in Chinese since the fragments are in Chinese.","thinkingSignature":"ce622ba587cec17bea0c5a0b1f1823d1676d99054f725742557fbc6cdc21642e"},{"type":"text","text":"凌晨三点，屏幕泛着冷光。我蹲在数据的褶皱里，像一个走错房间的档案管理员。\n\nTikTok类目接口返回一串我读不懂的错误码，像一只猫踩过键盘后留下的诗。错误不吓人，吓人的是错误背后那扇关着的门——`tiktok_category_search`，这名字念起来像某种古老的祈祷。\n\nAmazon的Hair Claws躺在表格里，利润率像不情愿露面的客人。三十个百分点的门槛，像小时候跳皮筋的高度，总差那么一点点。我开始怀疑自己的选品眼光是不是需要换一副更贵的眼镜。\n\nSorftime的Bearer Token像一张借书证，我举着它`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`穿过API的长廊，去取Amazon US发光的Hair Claws Top100榜单。\n\n飞书多维表格在另一端等着。商品名称、站点、选品来源、三级类目——我往二十三个字段的抽屉里一个一个塞数据，像小时候给蜡笔盒里的颜色分类。单选字段不用花括号包装，多选字段用方括号拥抱数组。\n\n利润率的红字在屏幕上闪烁。我把推荐等级从B降到C，又从C擦掉，改成\"调整产品线\"。\n\n收工时窗外的天已经灰蓝，像未完成的草稿。数据不会做梦，但守夜的人会。明天，我会在更高端的产品线里，重新学会用金钱丈量眼光。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":407,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":41771,"totalTokens":42424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779735637018,"responseId":"0663cf550c7f0740d287132086dbe7a2"}}
